<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div><div>The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our attention which may affect your children.</div><div><br></div><div>I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of influenza in a pupil in one of our Year 3 classes. Influenza is an infectious illness that is caused by a virus which affects the respiratory system â€“ nose, throat and lungs. It is spread by droplets from someone who is coughing or through contact. Small children are very susceptible as they touch everything and are constantly putting their hands onto their face and into their&nbsp;mouth. Symptoms include: fever, body aches, chills, dizziness, headaches, nausea, vomiting, sore throat,&nbsp;runny nose and fatigue. Please seek immediate medical advice and advise the school promptly if your child is&nbsp;unwell with any of the above symptoms.</div><div><br></div><div>At school, we are taking all precautions necessary including:</div><div><ul><li>Implementing good hygiene measures</li><li>Daily cleaning and disinfection of surfaces, door handles, stair railings, toys, bathroom accessories&nbsp;and food utensils</li><li>Unwell children will see nurse and if necessary parents will be contacted</li><li>The children have been taught how to wash their hands by teachers and also how to cover their&nbsp;mouths and noses when coughing or sneezing</li></ul><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If you believe your child has influenza, please seek medical treatment, follow safety procedures at home and&nbsp;keep them away from school until they have recovered from the illness.</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div>For further information about influenza, please see <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Flu/Pages/Introduction.aspx">this link</a></div><div><br></div></span></font></div><span lang="en-GB"><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><div style="margin: 0px;"><div style="margin: 0px;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px;">Warm regards,<br><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;">Janet Brock</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>Head Teacher</b></div></div></div><br></font></div></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><br></p></div></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
